data.description: This home has it all! In the excellent Long Beach school district & the desired Old Town Gardens subdivision. This full brick, 3 bed and 2 full bath home features tray ceilings in the living room and primary bedroom. Smart house upgrades like a Ring doorbell, keyless entry, and light switches controlled by an App also installed. Gather around the wood burning fireplace or enjoy the large, completely fenced backyard & side patio. 3 different gates allow options for backyard storage and activities. The yard backs up to a city easement, giving the owner a way to access the backyard & park a boat or RV! (see photos) Solar lights mounted to privacy fence as well as motion sensor outdoor lights. Come see this perfect home today!
